race.comment: BUTTERFLIES LAD (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.73) in a Grade 5 at Warrnambool. Solid record here winning four races. Key runner on his best form. WITH THE WIND (1) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Missed the frame latest (23.23) when eighth over 390m at Ballarat in a Grade 5. Among the main chances. CRACKERJACK BERN (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Ballarat behind Pyrenees Ace (22.72) in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Hard to beat again.
